ingredientsDesc:
1. PCR Tray with pre-aliquoted and dried SSP Primer Mixes
Each well in the PCR tray contains a dried SSP primer solution consisting of allele-and/or group-specific primers as well as a control primer pair matching non-allelic sequences.
2. PCR Caps
3. Master Mix
Three 1.8ml vials of ready to  use 1 x concentration containing the PCR buffer (Tris-HCI, KCI, Gelatin), MgCl2, nucleotides (dATP, dCTP, dGTP, dTTP), glycerol and cresol red. The Master Mix has been optimized for use with AmpliTaq DNA Polymerase (Roche Molecular System, Inc.)
4. Product Instructions For Use/Batch Specific Product Information Booklet\n5. Interpretation worksheet
